snippet.title: Cold Front | RPG Maker Horror | No Commentary
snippet.description:
Game: Cold Front
Find the game here: https://racheldrawsthis.itch.io/cold-front
Original creator: RachelDrawsThis
Release Date: 2022
Engine: RPG Maker MV
I do NOT own anything on this video, all credit to their respective creators.

If the creator wants me to take this down, please tell me.
もしクリエイターがこれを削除することを望むなら、私に言ってほしい。 (DeepL)

Endings Gotten: 1/2

Snowing in July, seems like a normal Finnish summer to me haha (jk, it was actually quite hot the past summer but thats for certain... reasons. most people know.)

A neat game as always which kind of hit too close to home haha. I liked this. Art is good and I liked the story. Good message I think.

I don't bother a lot with descriptions anymore haha so send a frog if you read this far.
